name: SMSmessagetracking_backup_exclusao
queryText:
SELECT
    a.SubscriberKey,
    b.MobileMessageTrackingID,
    b.EID,
    b.MID,
    b.Mobile,
    b.MessageID,
    b.KeywordID,
    b.CodeID,
    b.ConversationID,
    b.CampaignID,
    b.Sent,
    b.Delivered,
    b.Undelivered,
    b.Outbound,
    b.Inbound,
    b.CreateDateTime,
    b.ModifiedDateTime,
    b.ActionDateTime,
    b.MessageText,
    b.IsTest,
    b.MobileMessageRecurrenceID,
    b.ResponseToMobileMessageTrackingID,
    b.IsValid,
    b.InvalidationCode,
    b.SendID,
    b.SendSplitID,
    b.SendSegmentID,
    b.SendJobID,
    b.SendGroupID,
    b.SendPersonID,
    b.SubscriberID,
    b.SMSStandardStatusCodeId,
    b.Description,
    b.Name,
    b.ShortCode,
    b.SharedKeyword,
    b.Ordinal,
    b.FromName,
    b.JBActivityID,
    b.JBDefinitionID
FROM Exclusao_contatos a
    INNER JOIN _smsmessagetracking b 
        ON a.SubscriberKey = b.SubscriberKey
